1) Drink plenty of water
2) Open windows and turn on fan to improve air circulation
3) Turn off distractions like cellphone, internet, etc.
4) Decrease sugar intake
5) Do not multi task and focus on one thing
6) Make a plan on what to accomplish for the day
7) Change environment, go to library or coffee shop
8) Get plenty of sleep
9) Establish deadlines
10) Make yourself comfortable but not too much
